UEFI:

Modern firmware interface
Supports large hard drives and GPT disks
Supports both 32-bit and 64-bit systems
Graphical interface with mouse support
Secure Boot feature for firmware integrity
More extensive configuration options
Faster boot times
Supports plugins and drivers for hardware
Legacy Compatibility Mode available



BIOS:

Legacy firmware interface
Limited to 2.2TB boot drive capacity and MBR
Primarily supports 16-bit systems
Text-based interface with keyboard navigation
Limited security features
Limited configuration settings
Slower boot times
Limited to firmware updates
No Compatibility Mode
